-- =============================================================================
-- ECONOMY MONITOR
-- National economic statistics screen for the Quid state economy
--
-- Version: 0.3.1-ACTUAL
--
-- Purpose:
--   Read-only national statistics display for a large monitor.
--   This is NOT a banking UI, NOT a treasury controller, and NOT a leaderboard.
--
-- Shows:
--   - GDP graph + obvious current GDP figure in Q
--   - GDP per capita graph + obvious current GDP/capita figure in Q
--   - Inflation graph + obvious current inflation figure in percent
--   - CPI / purchasing power
--   - Wealth inequality aggregate statistics
--   - Monetary conditions
--   - National scale and policy indicators
--
-- Data behaviour:
--   1. Tries future official handler: { type = "national_statistics" }
--   2. Falls back to current server handlers: status, get_prices, list_accounts
--
-- Current backend limitations:
--   - GDP requires an official economic/output event ledger.
--   - CPI requires an official CPI basket and price data.
--   - Inflation requires CPI history.
--   - Policy rates require config/policy data.
-- =============================================================================

-- =============================================================================
-- CONFIG
-- =============================================================================
